{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd6db039a3","title":"杨成武对解放军测绘学院的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"76cbdfe8e0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":10,"articleId":"bd6db039a3"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e1397e909a","name":"杨成武","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"53bbb63fc8","name":"杨成武"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2c509271d","type":"title","text":"杨成武对解放军测绘学院的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"222c41edcc","type":"authors","text":"杨成武","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"a99bf0a61f","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：18时〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"48e82320ae","type":"paragraph","text":"学校大联合问题请李、王付总长抓一下，找测绘学院两派共同商量一下，让他们先行一步，做出个榜样来。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"396e4b082e","type":"paragraph","text":"总参首长指示：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"1083cfc446","type":"paragraph","text":"1、按班、队、系实行革命大联合和组成三结合领导班子。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"ca4bcb86cf","type":"paragraph","text":"2、关于复课闹革命问题，首先要复毛泽东思想的课。学习最新指示。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"f1c4bdf3d0","type":"paragraph","text":"商谈代表：两派派出相等数量的代表，各五人，主要勤务员要参加，包括参加组织的革命领导干部在内。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"},{"id":"56921c44d8","type":"paragraph","text":"院、部、系的领导干部，双方马上协商，只要双方能够同意的都可参加（数量不限）。如果部里找不出适当人时，处的干部也可以，部的最好有人参加，特别是院务部和政治部要有领导干部参加。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3"}],"page":{"id":"1a068c0250","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bd6db039a3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}